---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — TrackMarc Motorsport Photography"
  description="Marc Ronan — independent motorsport photographer based in Ireland, covering F1, WEC and GT racing across Europe."
>
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="about-role">Independent Motorsport Photographer</p>
      <h1>Marc<br /><em>Ronan</em></h1>

      <p>
        Based in Ireland and covering motorsport across Europe, I document the sport through a lens
        focused on raw speed, technical precision, and the moments that happen away from the podium.
      </p>

      <p>
        My work spans Formula racing, endurance classics, and national events — from the high-speed
        battles of Formula 2 at Monza, Zandvoort, and the Hungaroring, to the overnight endurance
        drama of the Le Mans 24 Hours at Circuit de la Sarthe.
      </p>

      <p>
        I shoot independently, building a portfolio that captures the intensity of motorsport as it
        actually is — the blur of a car at full throttle, the concentration in the garage, the light
        at dusk on a circuit that never sleeps.
      </p>

      <div class="about-section-title">Circuits Covered</div>
      <ul class="gear-list">
        <li>Autodromo Nazionale Monza — Formula 1 &amp; Formula 2</li>
        <li>Circuit Zandvoort — Formula 1 &amp; Formula 2</li>
        <li>Hungaroring, Budapest — Formula 1 &amp; Formula 2</li>
        <li>Circuit de la Sarthe, Le Mans — Le Mans 24 Hours</li>
        <li>Herbert Park, Dublin — Irish Motorsport</li>
        <li>Mondello Park, Co. Kildare — Irish Championship Circuit Racing (ICCR)</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="about-section-title">Series Followed</div>
      <ul class="gear-list">
        <li>FIA Formula 2 Championship</li>
        <li>FIA Formula 1 World Championship</li>
        <li>FIA World Endurance Championship</li>
        <li>GT World Challenge Europe</li>
        <li>Irish National Motorsport</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="accreditation-box" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        <h4>Seeking Media Accreditation</h4>
        <p>
          Actively building media credentials across FIA, ACO, and national series events.
          If you're a press officer, series coordinator, or team media manager and see potential
          in my work, I'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/gallery" class="btn btn-primary">View Gallery</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
